{"tid":730923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿蘇打《FIFA18》減壓 你估佢用邊隊？","createTime":"2018-07-05T20:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T02:48:58.000Z","uid":87072,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1f18291296321c032ffec3d4d1960266559a77b1","tid":730923,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/255/22055249255/22054468033_583x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F255%2F22055249255%2F22054468033_583x420.jpg&h=e0b1493f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=AL1i7qRJf9X35M36L0oE2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b80dbbad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】蘇亞雷斯於周五世盃8強硬撼法國前，與隊友一起打機減壓，更反映了他對前球會利物浦念念不忘。<br />\n<br />\n烏拉圭周五將會在世界盃8強對戰法國，大戰當前壓力在所難免，然而，烏拉圭前鋒蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）就自有減壓之道。<br />\n<br />\n從網上一段instagram片段顯示，「阿蘇」於大戰法國前選擇的減壓方式，是跟後備門將隊友馬田甘賓拿一起玩電玩足球遊戲《FIFA 18》，遊戲中蘇亞雷斯竟然大膽倒戈，以前東家利物浦對戰甘賓拿所選的巴塞隆拿，只見阿蘇全程玩得開心，完全沒有因為大戰當前而影響心情，亦顯出他對舊東家念念不忘。<br />\n<br />\n回說兩人於遊戲中的戰況，蘇亞雷斯明顯對利物浦的實力仍然瞭如指掌，在穆罕默德沙拿和佐敦軒達臣密密建功下，其領軍的利記竟以8:2大炒巴塞。"},{"pid":"7b9c564b33ddc013e721709fb6db43dc9c56b76f","tid":730923,"uid":2313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T21:04:18.000Z","msg":"259<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456a00acb71bab91b0094c77b13c500769963738","tid":730923,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T22:38:16.000Z","msg":"回家吧"},{"pid":"b3a3ec2f9648a9ea199e4aca67ea699e9278bbff","tid":730923,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"死25<br />\n仲要大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 